        "created_at": "2020-09-11T02:05:41.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Great note.  A bottle of the 2014 Roulot really opened up my eyes to what can be done with aligote.  (Had had a few previously, including Chevillon and the Lafarge mentioned by RichardP, that left me pretty nonplussed.)  Must be amazing with the additional age.</p>",
